Utterance.UttText: In bed 6 is Nina Fleming, 78 yrs old under Dr Angelika, She came in with cough, shallow breathing and complicated by her COPD.
She is not a smoker but her husband is.
She is on oxygen 3l/nasal prongs and she is on the same.
Still on puffers, antibiotics and she prefers upright position.
Otherwise she is ok. ambulant with walker with 1 assist.
